title: My Sweet Orange Tree (Meu Pé de Laranja Lima) (2012)

sources.title: MONBELORANGERBANDEANNONCE
sources.description: Marcos Bernstein My Sweet Orange Tree (Meu Pé de Laranja Lima) (2012) My Sweet Orange Tree (Meu Pé de Laranja Lima) directed by Marcos Bernstein Brazil, 2012 The film follows the story of Zezé, a little and very imaginative and sensitive but misunderstood boy.
